      "title": "Computer Numerical Control (CNC) Machinist",
      "description": "Aureol Global Connections is seeking experienced CNC Machinists on behalf of Gibney Steel Products Limited located at Moylagh, Oldcastle, Co. Meath, A82 KT97 to join their skilled production team. The successful candidate will be responsible for setting up and operating CNC machinery, including press brake machines, while interpreting production drawings to manufacture components to specification. The role also involves carrying out quality checks, meeting daily production targets, maintaining equipment and work areas, and strictly following all health and safety procedures. Candidates may also be required to work within our robotic welding cell (training provided) and carry out ad-hoc production duties as needed. The ideal candidate will have good attention to detail, the ability to follow instructions accurately, good teamwork and communication skills, and a reliable, safety-conscious attitude. Previous CNC or manufacturing experience is an advantage, but training will be provided for the suitable candidate. This is a full-time role of 48 hours per week with an annual salary range of €45,052.80-€48,000. Interested applicants should send their CV to info@aureolglobalconnections.com.",
